            "id": "devotion",
            "type": "devotion",
            "title": "Daily Devotional",
            "value": "%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20in%20the%20heart%20of%20all%20people%20a%20desire%20for%20a%20permanent%20relationship%20with%20God%20and%20a%20desire%20to%20dwell%20with%20Him%20forever.%20In%20this%20life%2C%20we%20are%20forever%20beset%20with%20a%20sense%20of%20impermanence%2C%20of%20being%20absent%20from%20the%20Lord.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThose%20who%20love%20God%20are%20running%20to%20Him%2C%20not%20from%20Him!%20They%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20way%20to%20dwell%20with%20Him.%20David's%20desire%20to%20build%20a%20house%20for%20God%20reflected%20his%20wish%20to%20have%20a%20permanent%20home%20with%20God.%20David%20had%20such%20a%20love%20for%20God's%20presence%20that%20he%20longed%20for%20God%20to%20have%20a%20permanent%20residence%20right%20next%20door%20to%20his%20palace.%20God%20responded%20to%20David's%20yearning%20by%20saying%20that%20He%20would%20provide%20a%20place%20for%20His%20people%20and%20plant%20them%20so%20they%20could%20have%20a%20home%20of%20their%20own.%20He%20also%20told%20David%20that%20He%20would%20build%20a%20house%20for%20him.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ETo%20meet%20someone%20is%20a%20temporary%20experience%2C%20but%20to%20live%20together%20with%20that%20person%20implies%20a%20permanent%20relationship.%20Jesus%20told%20His%20disciples%2C%20%22All%20those%20who%20love%20me%20will%20do%20what%20I%20say.%20My%20Father%20will%20love%20them%2C%20and%20we%20will%20come%20to%20them%20and%20live%20with%20them%22%20(John%2014%3A23).%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESettle%20in%20today%20in%20God's%20presence.%20His%20desire%20is%20to%20dwell%20with%20you%20forever!%20%3C%2Fp%3E%0A"
        },
        {
            "id": "ot-passage",
            "type": "passage",
            "title": "Old Testament Reading",
            "api_nlt_to_ref": "2Samuel.7:1-8:18",
            "value": "%3Cdiv%20class%3D%22%20NLT%20NLT%20BibleText%20section%22%3E%3Csection%3E%3Ch2%20class%3D%22bk_ch_vs_header%22%3E2%20Samuel%207%3A1-8%3A18%2C%20NLT%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_1%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%221%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22chapter-number%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw%22%3E2%20Samuel%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22cw_ch%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EThe%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22subhead-sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Covenant%20Promise%20to%20David%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-ch-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E1%3C%2Fspan%3EWhen%20King%20David%20was%20settled%20in%20his%20palace%20and%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20given%20him%20rest%20from%20all%20the%20surrounding%20enemies%2C%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_2%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%222%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E2%3C%2Fspan%3Ethe%20king%20summoned%20Nathan%20the%20prophet.%20%26%23x201C%3BLook%2C%26%23x201D%3B%20David%20said%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BI%20am%20living%20in%20a%20beautiful%20cedar%20palace%2C%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A2%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Hebrew%20%3Cem%3Ea%20house%20of%20cedar.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20but%20the%20Ark%20of%20God%20is%20out%20there%20in%20a%20tent!%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_3%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%223%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E3%3C%2Fspan%3ENathan%20replied%20to%20the%20king%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BGo%20ahead%20and%20do%20whatever%20you%20have%20in%20mind%2C%20for%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20is%20with%20you.%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_4%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%224%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E4%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20that%20same%20night%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20said%20to%20Nathan%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_5%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%225%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E5%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BGo%20and%20tell%20my%20servant%20David%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20has%20declared%3A%20Are%20you%20the%20one%20to%20build%20a%20house%20for%20me%20to%20live%20in%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_6%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%226%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E6%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20have%20never%20lived%20in%20a%20house%2C%20from%20the%20day%20I%20brought%20the%20Israelites%20out%20of%20Egypt%20until%20this%20very%20day.%20I%20have%20always%20moved%20from%20one%20place%20to%20another%20with%20a%20tent%20and%20a%20Tabernacle%20as%20my%20dwelling.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_7%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%227%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E7%3C%2Fspan%3EYet%20no%20matter%20where%20I%20have%20gone%20with%20the%20Israelites%2C%20I%20have%20never%20once%20complained%20to%20Israel%26%23x2019%3Bs%20tribal%20leaders%2C%20the%20shepherds%20of%20my%20people%20Israel.%20I%20have%20never%20asked%20them%2C%20%26%23x201C%3BWhy%20haven%26%23x2019%3Bt%20you%20built%20me%20a%20beautiful%20cedar%20house%3F%26%23x201D%3B%26%23x2019%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_8%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%228%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E8%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BNow%20go%20and%20say%20to%20my%20servant%20David%2C%20%26%23x2018%3BThis%20is%20what%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20of%20Heaven%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Armies%20has%20declared%3A%20I%20took%20you%20from%20tending%20sheep%20in%20the%20pasture%20and%20selected%20you%20to%20be%20the%20leader%20of%20my%20people%20Israel.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_9%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%229%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E9%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20have%20been%20with%20you%20wherever%20you%20have%20gone%2C%20and%20I%20have%20destroyed%20all%20your%20enemies%20before%20your%20eyes.%20Now%20I%20will%20make%20your%20name%20as%20famous%20as%20anyone%20who%20has%20ever%20lived%20on%20the%20earth!%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_10%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2210%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E10%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20I%20will%20provide%20a%20homeland%20for%20my%20people%20Israel%2C%20planting%20them%20in%20a%20secure%20place%20where%20they%20will%20never%20be%20disturbed.%20Evil%20nations%20won%26%23x2019%3Bt%20oppress%20them%20as%20they%26%23x2019%3Bve%20done%20in%20the%20past%2C%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_11%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2211%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E11%3C%2Fspan%3Estarting%20from%20the%20time%20I%20appointed%20judges%20to%20rule%20my%20people%20Israel.%20And%20I%20will%20give%20you%20rest%20from%20all%20your%20enemies.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%26%23x201C%3B%26%23x2018%3BFurthermore%2C%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20declares%20that%20he%20will%20make%20a%20house%20for%20you%26%23x2014%3Ba%20dynasty%20of%20kings!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_12%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2212%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E12%3C%2Fspan%3EFor%20when%20you%20die%20and%20are%20buried%20with%20your%20ancestors%2C%20I%20will%20raise%20up%20one%20of%20your%20descendants%2C%20your%20own%20offspring%2C%20and%20I%20will%20make%20his%20kingdom%20strong.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_13%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2213%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E13%3C%2Fspan%3EHe%20is%20the%20one%20who%20will%20build%20a%20house%26%23x2014%3Ba%20temple%26%23x2014%3Bfor%20my%20name.%20And%20I%20will%20secure%20his%20royal%20throne%20forever.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_14%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2214%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E14%3C%2Fspan%3EI%20will%20be%20his%20father%2C%20and%20he%20will%20be%20my%20son.%20If%20he%20sins%2C%20I%20will%20correct%20and%20discipline%20him%20with%20the%20rod%2C%20like%20any%20father%20would%20do.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_15%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2215%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E15%3C%2Fspan%3EBut%20my%20favor%20will%20not%20be%20taken%20from%20him%20as%20I%20took%20it%20from%20Saul%2C%20whom%20I%20removed%20from%20your%20sight.%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_16%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2216%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E16%3C%2Fspan%3EYour%20house%20and%20your%20kingdom%20will%20continue%20before%20me%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A16%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%20and%20some%20Hebrew%20manuscripts%3B%20Masoretic%20Text%20reads%20%3Cem%3Ebefore%20you.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20for%20all%20time%2C%20and%20your%20throne%20will%20be%20secure%20forever.%26%23x2019%3B%26%23x201D%3B%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_17%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2217%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-fl-sp%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E17%3C%2Fspan%3ESo%20Nathan%20went%20back%20to%20David%20and%20told%20him%20everything%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20had%20said%20in%20this%20vision.%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_18%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2218%22%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22subhead%22%3EDavid%26%23x2019%3Bs%20Prayer%20of%20Thanks%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22body-hd%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E18%3C%2Fspan%3EThen%20King%20David%20went%20in%20and%20sat%20before%20the%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%20and%20prayed%2C%3C%2Fp%3E%0A%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body-fl-sp%22%3E%26%23x201C%3BWho%20am%20I%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BSovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20and%20what%20is%20my%20family%2C%20that%20you%20have%20brought%20me%20this%20far%3F%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_19%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2219%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E19%3C%2Fspan%3EAnd%20now%2C%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20everything%20else%2C%20you%20speak%20of%20giving%20your%20servant%20a%20lasting%20dynasty!%20Do%20you%20deal%20with%20everyone%20this%20way%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BSovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%3F%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A19%3C%2Fspan%3E%20Or%20%3Cem%3EThis%20is%20your%20instruction%20for%20all%20humanity%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BSovereign%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ci%20class%3D%22tn-sc-ital%22%3ELord%3C%2Fi%3E%3Cem%3E.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_20%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2220%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E20%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BWhat%20more%20can%20I%20say%20to%20you%3F%20You%20know%20what%20your%20servant%20is%20really%20like%2C%20Sovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E.%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_21%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2221%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E21%3C%2Fspan%3EBecause%20of%20your%20promise%20and%20according%20to%20your%20will%2C%20you%20have%20done%20all%20these%20great%20things%20and%20have%20made%20them%20known%20to%20your%20servant.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_22%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2222%22%3E%0A%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%22ext-body%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E22%3C%2Fspan%3E%26%23x201C%3BHow%20great%20you%20are%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BSovereign%20%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E!%20There%20is%20no%20one%20like%20you.%20We%20have%20never%20even%20heard%20of%20another%20God%20like%20you!%20%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_23%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2223%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E23%3C%2Fspan%3EWhat%20other%20nation%20on%20earth%20is%20like%20your%20people%20Israel%3F%20What%20other%20nation%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3BGod%2C%20have%20you%20redeemed%20from%20slavery%20to%20be%20your%20own%20people%3F%20You%20made%20a%20great%20name%20for%20yourself%20when%20you%20redeemed%20your%20people%20from%20Egypt.%20You%20performed%20awesome%20miracles%20and%20drove%20out%20the%20nations%20and%20gods%20that%20stood%20in%20their%20way.%3Ca%20class%3D%22a-tn%22%3E*%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22tn-ref%22%3E7%3A23%3C%2Fspan%3E%20As%20in%20Greek%20version%20(see%20also%201%26%23xA0%3BChr%2017%3A21)%3B%20Hebrew%20reads%20%3Cem%3EYou%20made%20a%20name%20for%20yourself%20and%20awesome%20miracles%20for%20your%20land%20in%20the%20sight%20of%20your%20people%2C%20whom%20you%20redeemed%20from%20Egypt%2C%20the%20nations%20and%20their%20gods.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%20%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_24%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2224%22%3E%3Cspan%20class%3D%22vn%22%3E24%3C%2Fspan%3EYou%20made%20Israel%20your%20very%20own%20people%20forever%2C%20and%20you%2C%20O%26%23xA0%3B%3Cspan%20class%3D%22sc%22%3ELord%3C%2Fspan%3E%2C%20became%20their%20God.%3C%2Fverse_export%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%0A%3Cverse_export%20orig%3D%22sam2_7_25%22%20bk%3D%22sam2%22%20ch%3D%227%22%20vn%3D%2225%22%